Add property/keywords to tools
- set list of keywords
    - desktop/ mobile
    - high latency/ high throughput
    - optimized/ highly optimized
    - rest-api/ graphql/ protobuf
    - etc

Assign using LLM like with categories
Have a set list and assign those keywords to a tool at the same time (more or less) as categories are assigned
A tool can have multiple keywords, and should contain as many as apply

The list of keywords should be comprehensive and extensive

If there are problems with implementation, please ask
